Hello,

Thank you for your time today.
I could download the attached log files and after checking them I could see that the period for which it doesn't open the hyperlink is related to the scanning of the location C:/PST.
Regarding this, I would like you to please try to exclude the extensions .ost and .pst (Outlook archives) from the scanning.
You can do this from the Settings (depending which apply to your computer - Global or Custom) -> File Tracing and Shadowing.
[Inline image name : image016.png]

You would need to update the policies and restart Outlook after saving.
Please let me know if the performance improved after that.

Best regards,
Alin Anca
